info.name: e-Proof Issuer API Collection
info.description:
This collection is aimed to provide a convenient and user-friendly way for issuers to try out the e-Proof API, please check with the e-Proof Issuer Manual for the detailed API description.

For the access tokens. When you run the request "\[#3.1\] \[AUTH-001 \*\] getAccessToken," the access token will be automatically refreshed that you don't have to worry about manually updating tokens when they expire.

For the one time setup purpose APIs (3.\* series). These APIs are essential for the initial setup of your issuer account. A demo request and response offer a practical example that showcases the expected data formats, response structures, and any additional parameters required for a successful integration.
